        "subject": "LU-2683 lov: release all locks in closure to release sublock",
        "message": "LU-2683 lov: release all locks in closure to release sublock\n\nWe used to only release current parent lock, this may cause deadlock\nif the sublock is shared. See stacktrace of LU-2683 and LU-874 for\ndetails.\n\nThis is the b2_1 back-port of original/master patch from Jinshan\nand already for LU-2683, with Gerrit change Id\nIbe5fc364ef22a279f23bb24ad1311a1ad09be369 at\nhttp://review.whamcloud.com/5208 (patch-set #2).\n\nLustre-change: http://review.whamcloud.com/5208/\n\nSigned-off-by: Bruno Faccini <bruno.faccini@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I264a6039a977e7826e1b22474dc635b61163efbd\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/b2_1"
